       <div id="quick_links">
        <h3>
         Updated UTHSC Faculty Handbook
        </h3>
        <p>
         The
         <strong>
          <a href="/docs/2018-August-UTHSC-Faculty-Handbook-final.pdf" target="_blank">
           UTHSC Faculty Handbook
          </a>
         </strong>
        </p>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </body>
</html>
has been revised, effective August 2018. Download a copy of this new version today for the latest information that has been changed including (1) replacement of Cumulative Performance Review (CPR) with Enhanced Post-Tenure Performance Review (EPPR), (2) required edits for campus tenure review procedures to comply with the Board of Trustees policy, (3) insertion of anonymous voting throughout, and (4) revision of language for Visiting Professors and Distinguished Visiting Professors.
<p>
 To clearly delineate the August 2018 revision from the prior December 2015 version, the document now has (1) an updated last revision date of August 2018 in the footer, (2) Calibri 11 font, versus Times New Roman 12, and (3) a new cover page. The document also now contains an Appendix M (procedure for EPPR).
</p>
<p>
 It is important to note that additional areas in the Faculty Handbook are being worked on to align them with the requirements of the most recent Board of Trustees
 <em>
  Policies on Academic Freedom, Responsibility and Tenure.
 </em>
 As noted in Section 1.4 of the UTHSC Faculty Handbook - when the Board of Trustees acts to change official University policies and procedures, such changes become effective on the date designatd by the Board of Trustees and those supersede any provision of the Faculty Handbook to the contrary without need for further notice. Download a copy of the Board's most recent
 <a href="https://universitytennessee.policytech.com/dotNet/documents/?docid=318&amp;public=true" target="_blank">
  <strong>
   Policies on Academic Freedom, Responisibility and Tenure (effective March 2018)
  </strong>
  .
 </a>
</p>
<h3>
 2018-2019 Faculty Evaluation Calendar Posted
</h3>
<p>
 Visit the
 <a href="/faculty/info.php">
  <strong>
   Faculty Information
  </strong>
 </a>
 section of our website for the Faculty Evaluation Calendar that provides dates for a variety of faculty processes as well as other important documents for faculty recruitment, appointment, promotion, tenure, and annual performance and planning review.
</p>
<h3>
 Policies and Procedures
</h3>
<p>
 Our policies and procedures have been incorporated into UTHSC's new policy management system. Visit
 <a href="https://uthsc.policymedical.net/" target="_blank">
  <strong>
   https://uthsc.policymedical.net/
  </strong>
 </a>
 for a link to all UTHSC policies and procedures. Contact us if you have questions or can't locate something you were looking for.
</p>
<p>
 Please note that you are NOT required to have a username and password to access documents in the PolicyManager system.
</p>
